-- Lions Gate raises FY07 revenue, free cash forecasts
-- 
-- Mon Feb 12, 2007 9:46am EST
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2007/02/12/us-lionsgate-forecast-idUSN1225666520070212

 

 LOS ANGELES  (Reuters) - Lions Gate Entertainment Corp. ( LGF.N ) raised its fiscal year 2007 revenue forecast to $950 million, from a previous estimate of over $900 million, Chief Executive Jon Feltheimer said on a conference call with analysts on Monday. 


 The independent film and television company also expects free cash flow of $100 million for the fiscal year, up from a previous estimate of over $85 million, Feltheimer said.